<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Exo+2:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <title>Dashboard</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Exo 2', sans-serif;
            background-image: linear-gradient(to right,#FFCC00, #FFBC4C,#FFDE63,#FEFFC4);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        header {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 16px 24px 16px 24px;
            position: relative;
        }
        header::before{
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -4px;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            background-color: #021024;
            height: 2px;
            border-radius: 1em;

        }
        .brand {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #021024;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }
        .user-actions {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 2px;
        }
        .user-name {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #021024;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }
        .logout {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #fff;
            background: #e53935;
            padding: 6px 16px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: background 0.2s;
        }
        .logout:hover {
            background: #b71c1c;
        }
        h2 {
            font-size: 32px;
            text-align: center;
            color: black;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }
        .container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
            background-color: transparent;
        }
        .details {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
            border-radius: 1em;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px 0 rgba(2,16,36,0.10);
            padding: 32px 28px 24px 28px;
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 100%;
            color: black;
            height: 400px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(100px);
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #021024;
            font-size: 1rem;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        a{
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #021024;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="brand">She Can Foundation</div>
        <div class="user-actions">
            <span class="user-name"><%= user.name %></span>
            <a href="/leaderboard" id="leader">LeaderBoard</a>
            <a href="/logout" class="logout">Logout</a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <h2>Welcome <%= user.name %></h2>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="details">
            <article>
                Hello Mr/Mrs. <%= user.name %>, we are glad to see you here. You are a part of our She Can Foundation. You were supposed to 
                rise funds to support the education of a girl child.
            </article>
            <p>This is your referral code, please use this referral code to raise the funds</p>
            <strong>Referral code: <%= user.referal_code %></strong>
            <p>Every contribution, no matter how small, can spark a wave of change for girls and women everywhere. 
                By raising funds to support initiatives that empower and educate, we can help break the cycle of poverty and discrimination. 
                Your efforts can provide essential resources, such as scholarships, health services, and vocational training, that enable young girls and women to realize their dreams and potential. 
                Together, we can create a brighter future, ensuring that every girl child has the opportunity to thrive and every woman can live her life with dignity and purpose. 
                Join us in this vital mission and make a difference today!</p>
            <div class="fund">
            <h3>Current Fund</h3>
            <p>Funds raised by using your referal code.</p>   
            <p>Current fund raised: â‚¹ <%= total_donations %></p>
        </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <footer class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2025 She Can Foundation</p>
    </footer>